OL,3,CChildcare cost protesters tell
OL,4,CExecutive 'enough is enough'
OL,6,FMore than 1,000 parents and children
OL,7,Fhave demonstrated in Belfast over
OL,8,Frising childcare costs.
OL,10,FThe colourful protest saw the
OL,11,Fdemonstrators marching through Belfast
OL,12,Fwith balloons, placards and prams,
OL,13,Fcalling for immediate supports for
OL,14,Fparents.
OL,16,FCurrently, parents in Northern Ireland
OL,17,Fcan use some supports including tax
OL,18,Fcredits.However, there is no scheme in
OL,19,Fplace for free childcare in Northern
OL,20,FIreland, unlike in England where 30
OL,21,Fhours are offered per week.
