OL,6,FStormont parties have placed a focus
OL,7,Fon prioritising childcare and, earlier
OL,8,Fthis year, education minister Paul
OL,9,FGivan said a new early learning and
OL,10,Fchildcare strategy for Northern
OL,11,FIreland could cost #400 million a year.
OL,13,FOfficials have said that progress on
OL,14,Fthe strategy will ultimately depend on
OL,15,Fthe availability of Executive funds.
