OL,6,FFinancial challenges and pressures
OL,7,Facross Northern Ireland's public
OL,8,Fservices have also led Stormont's
OL,9,Fleaders to request face-to-face talks
OL,10,Fwith Prime Minister Rishi Sunak as
OL,11,Fthey continue to press the Government
OL,12,Ffor more funding.Saturday's march was
OL,13,Forganised by Melted Parents NI which
OL,14,Fsays urgent action is needed.
OL,16,FThe group's founder Casey McGivern
OL,17,Fsaid the turnout shows the "power of
OL,18,Fparents" as she issued a warning to
OL,19,Fpoliticians.
