OL,6,FShe said: "Parents have been
OL,7,Fpolitically engaged and activated by
OL,8,Fthis cause and I would tell our
OL,9,Fparents: Pay attention.
OL,11,F"Because if you're not taking action
OL,12,Fto support families you're going to
OL,13,Ffeel it at election."
OL,15,FA spokesperson for the Department of
OL,16,FEducation said the education minister
OL,17,Fhas made the development of an early
OL,18,Flearning and childcare strategy a "top
OL,19,Fpriority".
