OL,3,CChildcare cost protesters tell
OL,4,CExecutive 'enough is enough'
OL,6,F"He is acutely aware that the cost of
OL,7,Fchildcare puts immense strain on
OL,8,Ffamily finances and, in some cases,
OL,9,Fprevents parents from entering and
OL,10,Fremaining in the workforce," they said.
OL,12,F"The minister is committed to
OL,13,Fdelivering a bespoke and affordable
OL,14,Fscheme for Northern Ireland that
OL,15,Faddresses the challenges that we face
OL,16,Fand delivers the outcomes that we want
OL,17,Fto achieve.
