OL,6,F"He appreciates that putting in place
OL,7,Fthe full infrastructure required will
OL,8,Ftake time and so is also considering
OL,9,Fwhat short-term measures might be
OL,10,Fpossible to ease current pressures."
OL,12,FIt continued: "DE officials, in
OL,13,Fconjunction with colleagues in other
OL,14,Fdepartments, are actively considering
OL,15,Fwhat measures would be possible and
OL,16,Fappropriate to ease the childcare
OL,17,Fpressures which parents are facing.
OL,19,F"A thorough assessment of all relevant
OL,20,Fevidence is a core component of this
OL,21,Fwork.
